  "title": "Salesforce Developer",
  "description": "<p>We require Salesforce developers for a Salesforce-based large-scale CRM implementation project (that will have both agile development and maintenance scope of work)</p><p><strong> Technical Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in Salesforce development (Apex, Visualforce, Lightning Components)</li><li>Experience with Salesforce configuration and customisation</li><li>Experience with Salesforce Public Sector Solution and Education Cloud.</li><li>Knowledge of Salesforce integrations and APIs</li><li>Salesforce Platform Developer/ admin certification</li><li>Familiar with agile development</li><li>Candidates with good Service Cloud experience and Education Cloud can be considered too.</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Min 6 years of Salesforce development experience,  with at least 1 year of Public Sector Solution and Education Cloud experience.</li><li>At least 3 years of agile development experience</li></ul><p></p>",
